Asuka Sakai (境亜寿香, Sakai Asuka) is a Japanese composer and musician working for NAMCO. She's best known for her works on various soundtracks from the 塊魂 (Katamari Damacy) and Ridge Racer video game series. She has released 2 albums to date on the IRMA records label and now mainly works in music production for games and anime.

She has contributed music to the following games:
- Ace Combat 3
- Libero Grande 2
- R4: Ridge Racer Type 4
- Klonoa 2: Lunatea's Veil
- Panikuru Panekuru
- Katamari Damacy
- Soul Caliber II

Miku joined the idol unit [StylipS](https://anilist.co/staff/111177) on April 27, 2013 and is one half of its subunit, [Pyxis](https://anilist.co/staff/139753), along with [Moe Toyota](https://anilist.co/staff/118398). 

Miku's hobbies include watching anime, dancing, and playing Hyakunin Isshu. She also practices kendo (but is at the lowest level) and enjoys acting. She is a fan of Kamen Rider, and her favorite rider is Den-O.
